Basement for the wine maker of this village. Bottom corner connects to kid's cave.
Around here somewhere is where the MC bust's the kid's attempt

A place kids can go if they want to "Run away" where adults
will feel safe letting them go to. Often just takes a day or two
for kids to feel comfortable going back home again.
Something one of the kids brought down, basically a world map
with a whole bunch of scribbles on it showing where that kid
wants to go when they become an adventurer.
______ often brings medicine and purified water for the kids
to use. Kids often love her because of that.
